snippet.title: Dungeonborne - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Dungeonborne is an immersive first-person PvPvE dungeon crawler. Venture solo or with trusted companions to hunt for treasure, explore ominous dungeons, and battle terrifying monsters and other cunning adventurers. Then escape before being consumed by darkness and greed.

Play the open alpha of Dungeonborne between February 2nd-12th during Steam Next Fest.

Discover more at https://dungeonborne.com/

Join us:
Discord: https://discord.gg/dungeonborne
Twitter: https://twitter.com/dungeonborne
Facebook: https://facebook.com/dungeonborne
Instagram: https://instagram.com/dungeonborne
